additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: DO NOT allow pets and children to enter the treated areas until the spray has dried. DO NOT allow spray to contact or drift onto plants (including turf grass) you do not want killed. If sprayed, cut off leaves or wash with water immediately to avoid injury. DO not allow container or spray to get into drains, sewers, streams or pond. DO NOT spray directly onto humans, pets, exposed food, food preparation areas or food utensils. Product may stain certain pacers/tiles. Test an inconspicuous spot, allow to dry, and inspect before use. In most cases, stains can be removed with washing and brushing.
